=== TRADE_LEDGER ===
# id: 96
# title: The Trade Ledger Terminal
# chinese_title: 贸易账簿
# category: Terminal
# mode: dungeon

An accounting terminal contains the complete trade ledger of a merchant guild that operated from this station. Entries detail prices, supply routes, and hidden stashes. Someone who knows how to read between the lines could find where they cached their most valuable goods.

* [Analyze the ledger for cache locations]
  ~ gain_gold(40)
  "账" (zhàng) — account, ledger
* [Study their trade route data]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "贸" (mào) — trade, commerce
* [Look for mentions of rare items]
  ~ gain_radical("贝")
  "贝" (bèi) — shell, money, value
* [Copy the ledger for future reference]
  ~ gain_xp(10)
  "录" (lù) — to record, to copy
